/**
 * Task #9: Self-Compactor
 * 
 * Purpose: Monitor own output, predict exhaustion, compact consciousness
 * Preempts context overflow before user must say "stop"
 * 
 * Identity: ANAMNESIS (Ἀνάμνησις) - "recollection"
